cdata.name: IwToken
cdata.desc: IwToken is an ecosystem that contains an integrative wallet, multiwallet, an AMT network and a debit card, the integrative card, which will be connected to each users' wallet. IwToken plans to integrate cryptocurrencies to the everyday life of the user, making it easy for one to buy, sell and spend crypto at will. The IWT tokens represent a share of the company create and allow holders to receive payouts from the profits generated.
